ain has inrecent months also seen a steep rise in bedbugs, with experts chalking it up to the creatures hiding in secondhand furniture and increased travel post-pandemic.\", \"from\": 1280, \"to\": 1649, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1297, \"end\": 1300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Health_Service\", \"score\": 0.9992372173521552, \"rank\": 0.0007633627270374778, \"text\": \"NHS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Health_Service\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Health_Service\"}, {\"begin\": 1373, \"end\": 1383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JavaScript\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.024010116989347e-17, \"text\": \"JavaScript\", \"types\": [\"Q9143\", \"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JavaScript\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JavaScript\"}, {\"begin\": 1445, \"end\": 1450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HTML5\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.8391353306797634e-14, \"text\": \"HTML5\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HTML5\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HTML5\"}, {\"begin\": 1466, \"end\": 1473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_Music_Up_Next\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Up Next\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_Music_Up_Next\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_Music_Up_Next\"}, {\"begin\": 1475, \"end\": 1482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.999997260851728, \"rank\": 2.596081784976924e-06, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"signs\", \"from\": 1301, \"to\": 1306}, {\"ngram\": \"bedbugs\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1317}, {\"ngram\": \"the home\", \"from\": 1321, \"to\": 1329}, {\"ngram\": \"this video\", \"f